.SH "Toolbox"
.PP
A \&.NET 10 library providing base services, telemetry, and dependency injection extensions\&.
.SH "Features"
.PP
.IP "\(bu" 2
\fBCryptography Services\fP: AES, RSA, and Base64 encoding/decoding
.IP "\(bu" 2
\fBFile Transfer Services\fP: FTP, FTPS, and SFTP with batch operations
.IP "\(bu" 2
\fBMailing Services\fP: SMTP with TLS/SSL, OAuth2, and attachment support
.IP "\(bu" 2
\fBAPI Services\fP: HTTP client with multiple authentication modes and retry policies
.IP "\(bu" 2
\fBLDAP Services\fP: Active Directory, Azure AD, OpenLDAP, and Apple Directory with advanced authentication (Kerberos, NTLM, Certificate, SASL) and management operations (enable/disable accounts, group membership, password reset, object movement)
.IP "\(bu" 2
\fBSSO Services\fP: Single Sign-On session management, automatic token refresh, and secure credential storage (Windows Credential Manager, encrypted file)
.IP "\(bu" 2
\fBDisposable Services\fP: Thread-safe base classes for synchronous and asynchronous disposal
.IP "\(bu" 2
\fBOpenTelemetry Integration\fP: Built-in distributed tracing and metrics collection
.IP "\(bu" 2
\fBDependency Injection\fP: Fluent extensions for easy service registration
.IP "\(bu" 2
\fBComprehensive Documentation\fP: Full Doxygen documentation (HTML, LaTeX, XML, DocBook, RTF, Man)
.PP
.SH "Requirements"
.PP
.IP "\(bu" 2
\&.NET 10\&.0 or later
.IP "\(bu" 2
C# 14\&.0
